README

Installation
------------

Ensure the following dependencies are satisfied:

- Autoconf
- Automake
- D-Bus*
- GCC
- libjson+
- libmount*
- libutil+
- libxfs*
- Make
- OpenSSL*
- pkg-config

* Development version required
+ From Glacier project

Run the following commands to build and install the library:

./bootstrap
./configure
make
sudo make install
(optional) make distclean

Uninstallation
--------------

Run the following commands to uninstall the library:

(if "make distclean" run) ./bootstrap
(if "make distclean" run) ./configure
(if "make distclean" run) make
sudo make uninstall
